snippet.title: SNES Longplay [318] Dragon Quest VI (Fan Translation) (part 1 of 7)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Valis77
This game is Fan-Translated the game is 95% finished but it was more then enough to make the game fully playable.

  As usual i do off screen levels as well as job classes when i enter or exit a town/castle which explains me getting spells and skill. Not to mention the item i get from spoils from beating certian monsters off screen. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
